Type: Package
Package: stabli
Title: Statistical Tables and Lists Thereof
Version: 0.3.0.4
Authors@R:
    person("Joonas", "Miettinen", , "joonas.miettinen@cancer.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8624-6754"))
Description: Create and make use of a more formal definition of a table of
    statistics. Store metadata such as the names of stratifying and value
    columns into the object itself so you don't have to keep track
    yourself. Easily write functions to produce statistical tables.
